title: War of the Roses: She Saw Him With His Fiance
description: Amanda started dating a guy and when she told her friend about him, her friend swears she knows him and that he's engaged but they couldn't find anything on social media about it.  Amanda confronted him about being engaged and he swore he wasn't.  But then she was in Office Depot one day and saw this...
